{"tid":2382681,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"下月起綜援生果金加薪2.7%，高額長生津加薪至$3815","createTime":"2021-01-27T12:14:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T13:33:34.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e46b8252a045c084521732f785d98715487f8f89","tid":2382681,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T12:14:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/下月起綜援生果金調高2-7-高額長生津加至-3815-083619051.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%88%E8%B5%B7%E7%B6%9C%E6%8F%B4%E7%94%9F%E6%9E%9C%E9%87%91%E8%AA%BF%E9%AB%982-7-%E9%AB%98%E9%A1%8D%E9%95%B7%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%A5%E5%8A%A0%E8%87%B3-3815-083619051.html&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdn38q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=fa179ebe\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/下月起綜援生果金調高2-7-高額長生津加至-3815-083619051.html</a><br />\n<br />\n社會福利署今日（27日）公布，由下月1日起，按社會保障援助物價指數的變動，調高綜合社會保障援助（綜援）計劃的標準項目金額，以及公共福利金計劃下俗稱生果金的高齡津貼、長者生活津貼及傷殘津貼金額2.7%，其中一般長生津由2770港元，調高至2845港元，增加75港元；高額長生津則由3715港元，調高100港元至3815港元。此外，租金津貼最高金額亦按租金指數調高1.6%。<br />\n<br />\n社署指，政府早前按既定機制，因應社會保障援助物價指數的變動，建議把上述各金額調高2.7%，而建議已獲得立法會財務委員會通過。上述調整共惠及約138萬人，政府為此將每年額外投放14.48億港元。下月1日亦推行一系列改善綜援計劃的措施，包括推行「豁免計算入息」改善措施，以及把多項特別津貼擴展至合資格非長者健全受助人。<br />\n<br />\n下月1日起，綜援計劃下租金津貼亦將根據既定機制，按甲類消費物價指數中私人房屋租金指數的變動作出調整。租金津貼的最高金額將會調高1.6%。單身人士租津為2515港元，2人至6人或以上家庭，租津由4440港元至7800港元不等。<br />\n<br />\n綜援金經調整後，65歲以下的健全成人單身人士，可獲的綜援金由2615港元，增加70港元至2685港元，健全兒童及不超過2名健全家庭成員的綜援金則由2605港元增加70港元至2675港元。<br />\n<br />\n俗稱生果金的高齡津貼亦由1435港元，增加了40港元至1475港元。至於普通傷殘津貼，金額亦由1835港元，增加了50港元至1885港元；而高額傷殘津貼，亦由3670港元，增加了100港元至3770港元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/IML0qwfL55KwffxNE0Qxlg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEyNDkuMjMwNzY5MjMwNzY5Mw--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/x9zeWanPGDXJiQS1XKGLPQ--~B/aD0xMDE1O3c9NzgwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/09cd23ba06415f20b558e21d053a01c6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FIML0qwfL55KwffxNE0Qxlg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEyNDkuMjMwNzY5MjMwNzY5Mw--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fx9zeWanPGDXJiQS1XKGLPQ--~B%2FaD0xMDE1O3c9NzgwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F09cd23ba06415f20b558e21d053a01c6&h=9d5108a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"162200b0eebb561ae0895eeaf7ee4cc5d036a054","tid":2382681,"uid":142712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T12:18:08.000Z","msg":"拎綜援好過"},{"pid":"88de198d836c2f08acb1629203a0983ff4bafc44","tid":2382681,"uid":71502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T12:25:12.000Z","msg":"新移民真係大享世界"},{"pid":"cfb688e497cf5cf8b36141c927a8d781772c0244","tid":2382681,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T12:27:57.000Z","msg":"@老貓"},{"pid":"833c4c854623c586a69c27058adc48914f49381c","tid":2382681,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"162200b0eebb561ae0895eeaf7ee4cc5d036a054","tid":2382681,"uid":142712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T12:18:08.000Z","msg":"拎綜援好過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T12:28:20.000Z","msg":"唔係可以兩樣拎曬嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af089a7474a7c1c34586223a86e2e730ad12b398","tid":2382681,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88de198d836c2f08acb1629203a0983ff4bafc44","tid":2382681,"uid":71502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T12:25:12.000Z","msg":"新移民真係大享世界"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T12:29:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgur.dcard.tw/u5fdfia.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.dcard.tw%2Fu5fdfia.gif&h=b28c4db3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e6f3a284f4ee16d749df635b5b16f181b5611af","tid":2382681,"uid":63108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T12:40:39.000Z","msg":"仆街又追通漲"},{"pid":"1222